channel.title: Can anyone help me
channel.description:
i was following the 'how to make a server' guide and i made it through some steps i was on the portfowarding one i typed my i.p in the address bar then hit go, then came a box up it says type a username and password and i didnt know it so can anyone tell me the default one or if i have one tell me where to look to find it.
--megachill-- chill out man

item.title: Can anyone help me
item.dc:creator: @johno2 johno2
item.description:
@johno2 wrote:

If you can’t remember your password, at the back of your mode/router there is a restart button. Hole that in for 10 seconds and your whole internet is restarted, re-configure ur internet settings, and then you can create/leave the password to your liking.

item.title: Can anyone help me
item.dc:creator: @r34p4g3pk r34p4g3pk
item.description:
@r34p4g3pk wrote:

Your modem company allows changes to modem passwords without rights. If there is a “Forgot my password,” option somewhere on your default gateway, click that and change it to something you can easily remember, and if there isn’t something like that or you need special rights to change the password, yes, the defaults are admin and admin for the username and password.
